    "affected_lt": "4.8.2",
    "fixed_version": "4.8.2"
  },
  "analyst_note": "CVE-2018-12613 (PMASA-2018-4): Local file inclusion leading to RCE in phpMyAdmin 4.8.0-4.8.1. An authenticated attacker can include arbitrary PHP files via the target parameter. Fixed: 4.8.2.",
